528
00:29:10,359 --> 00:29:13,099
to get your block back.

529
00:29:16,329 --> 00:29:18,968
I'll show it to you after I eat this.

530
00:29:19,968 --> 00:29:22,509
Okay. Eat up.

531
00:29:24,678 --> 00:29:27,509
