535
00:29:43,158 --> 00:29:45,029
because he had no dad.

536
00:29:47,129 --> 00:29:48,198
Come in.

537
00:29:49,728 --> 00:29:51,339
Mr. Goo, I found it.

538
00:29:51,968 --> 00:29:53,967
I met the reporter who reported her disappearance...

539
00:29:53,968 --> 00:29:55,269
