00:30:11,559 --> 00:30:12,658
Du Na?

543
00:30:13,388 --> 00:30:14,559
They're the same person.

544
00:30:17,029 --> 00:30:18,329
How can this happen?

545
00:30:18,759 --> 00:30:20,059
How can this be real?

546
00:30:24,799 --> 00:30:25,968
