552
00:30:46,988 --> 00:30:48,359
That's an unlikely pair.

553
00:30:48,759 --> 00:30:51,629
She's suddenly so nice to him.

554
00:30:51,759 --> 00:30:52,829
Is she?

555
00:30:54,158 --> 00:30:55,329
That's a good thing.

556
00:30:56,099 --> 00:30:57,198
Yes.

557
00:31:02,569 --> 00:31:04,339
I guess so. Yes.

558
00:31:11,648 --> 00:31:12,748
Mr. Goo.

559
00:31:13,019 --> 00:31:15,348
I was on my way to say hello as this was day one...

560
00:31:15,349 --> 00:31:17,089
of our new department...

561
00:31:18,089 --> 00:31:20,488
as General Manager Hwang Jin Goo of the Travel Service Department.

